嘅時候好熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我頭先著緊短袖"},{"pid":"15117eff88667817775ab035953254068578fb5b","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd5d2e09e76bfb66c4b7b03fb752e0570ddb763","tid":2497180,"uid":262575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陣間使唔使滑雪返落去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"有人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我着雪鞋行上嚟所以要行返落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f7865ceea5287a3ca96b4b457ff0a5381abfba","tid":2497180,"uid":332128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁偏僻都有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980b9b120878363115be5d1f6a28e313646260b","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"真點上到頂！原來呢個先係頂<br />\n（而家已經落埋山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdswbc36cr9hQ1GgiUNLGqnCBKYXxWVgNkDmMThmMthyo?filename=EtC4FCo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtC4FCo.png&h=354a94e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係到望到瑞典<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/ball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;-ikea肉丸<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb51W2YDJGcJYhD1BPuxChjCNxw4CnB6ug4gEoKV6ALGr?filename=BqTzipE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqTzipE.png&h=704a6179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說上山嘅時候爆林行小路，見到hare腳印<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZtEG1Zi4Wa85JsDQrTXJmoVrJEVyyTxsNwF5ct92DeQg?filename=WQqNDqe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWQqNDqe.png&h=6daa128e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狐狸腳印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一串咁好優雅<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfYRCFjUJFJBwiBeozdbY8fGMGRJpZGkjSJiAzaWEz9T5?filename=XLAYK5j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXLAYK5j.png&h=f0a49cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有我嘅腳印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRD2F23pEpJj5c21PWMQ3nQniDwDbiAX7F6C77ZUYZCPh?filename=DT2sDqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT2sDqO.png&h=a6e3a5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落山決定行返大路落<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb3NmDfAc3kxSG5F5cJWfjXvpsTPWJFDppvtcdSd63F8U?filename=K6s8nSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6s8nSB.png&h=af0a3795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有蛋黃哥樣嘅山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcwBa9a38BWRiRT1hnS9Q1iVPmizMXzu5Ca42tSphQYfb?filename=Tqy7Drb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqy7Drb.png&h=129e53f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天使光環雲<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeU5iZAMGgypbj44Yq7JK58DboLgE1YfuRZFSLqPNrbaV?filename=WxhPRMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxhPRMc.png&h=10aaa0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魔鬼魚山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQbLsp1Ct56HdjSvcfWwmwb6h2Xeo5PHzfMgLwY9HMfTf?filename=WuYWwMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuYWwMd.png&h=52806ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安全落到山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmanLhFGzz5sn9QmGhyKxv3kcgQkhWb388ZoLrZzKEyhpK?filename=xAy7Dre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAy7Dre.png&h=f8b35e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人玩滑翔傘！應該係 我都想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3e4KZV7hbkz9CVY1DycoVkukLKhZPx3ijWmSccqsng1?filename=8EEOnSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EEOnSV.png&h=eac65a04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a5fc5352b2a7adbdf1c04e8ef6deb7502eec92e","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b0f7865ceea5287a3ca96b4b457ff0a5381abfba","tid":2497180,"uid":332128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁偏僻都有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"Yes芬蘭網絡覆蓋率差唔多100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828d6f8d85b78416ac0a4071edf94461e3c114d8","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbjLWFnuXpQ2TotK28CEc7FqKM9fXJwEhZhzh3dTRmL1M?filename=VPJO7nK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPJO7nK.png&h=0bfda4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成！！總共行咗12k，用咗六個鐘，郊遊速度加埋休息食嘢影相都算輕鬆行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲意猶未盡，可能今晚再去行吓第二座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家要焗桑拿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50750a5113aaee4fc95c04b84732962559ab14b2","tid":2497180,"uid":303821,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T16:13:33.000Z","msg":"好正，好想去外國行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb598e2c57206bd657fa5df44be305e69613ae16","tid":2497180,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:54:03.000Z","msg":"想試下行雪山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3892efc0cd1177d8244ff1ae36eb080ffd9da21","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"傍晚嘅時候又上多次山睇日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留咗係山兩個鐘諗住睇極光 但唔好彩佢哋無出現到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRSEjJtMSajL58FkTtzwZx18PobLnefADeJCdGk68ipKP?filename=2t9Saic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2t9Saic.jpg&h=9d166a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY36tQDotjLPWBBhSUfdpSmuDy4r8jYNDH7HA2EzFWWbZ?filename=1ebpLRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ebpLRz.jpg&h=af42dbb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a3f3c9fe011f128817abcfd019c8b38d09018d2","tid":2497180,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T06:48:37.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4eb8db691a22512a91244c8fe6d1a4a38a6a6ab5","tid":2497180,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"巴打幾好想像力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa910286e4eea6d9f7c867f02816b58d9539dce7","tid":2497180,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:51:10.000Z","msg":"雪山都收到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕唔怕死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871f3d86a99ae5a2a4632131e04db92ed6ed1d9e","tid":2497180,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34d7494f3a3065453addbc25c64ecda36c57872","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T11:1